Package: MitoPilot
Title: Mitogenome assembly, annotation, and curation
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Devin", "Leopold", , "devin.leopold@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Dan", "MacGuigan", , "daniel.macguigan@noaa.gov", role = "aut")
  )
Description: An R package for mitogenome assembly and annotation from
    genome skimming data that uses Nexflow and includes an R-Shiny app for
    project management and curation of results.
License: GPL (>= 3)
URL: https://github.com/Smithsonian/MitoPilot,
